org.hl7.vmr.r2

Class EvaluatedPerson

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hl7.vmr.r2.Entity
      • org.hl7.vmr.r2.Person
        • org.hl7.vmr.r2.EvaluatedPerson

  • public class EvaluatedPerson
extends Person
    A person who is the subject of evaluation by a CDS system. May be the focal patient or some other relevant person (e.g., a relative or a sexual contact). Includes demographic attributes, clinical statements, and related entities.

    Java class for EvaluatedPerson complex type.

         <element name="isDeceased" type="{urn:hl7-org:cdsdt:r2}BL" minOccurs="0"/>
